·        "Ferdinand Magellan" (1955)
·        "Captain of Dragoons" † (1956)
·        "The Long Bow" (1957)
·        "Mohawk Valley" † (1958)
·        "Captain of Foot" † (1959)
·        "Escape from France" † (1960)
·        "For the King" † (1961)[c]
·        "Nicholas Carey" † (1963)
·        "Bowman of Crécy" † (1966)
·        "The Hawk" † (1967)
·        "Sun of York" (1970)
·        "The Galleon" † (1971)
·        "Tank Commander" † (1972)
